task.summary: Default task

Made student request a dropdown of similar style to the teacher one and made the profile button work on student page.
Updated the student pass card so that it only has one fragment instead of 2.
General updates to forms
Updates to testmodels.py
Changed Pass model to three models

Fixed Pass functions (again) and html display
Fixed creation and request processes (request process is just as broken as before, no more no less)
Fixed some css problems with pass rendering (added float left)
Added template tag get_class to print text representation of the class name in template for pass type checking
Added new pass classes to admin panel
Fixed forms so that they work with the new setup
Unapproved passes show up now for teachers with new format

approve, checkout and checkin views now only work for the correct teacher
Updated teacher home with tabbing system and js
Fixed database
added the token authentication old users won't work until they are integreated (somehow) the old admin won't work with the api either
Added settings files and important modules for heroku
Fixed typo in base settings file and debug value checking
Fixed procfile (?)
Cleaned up python Deleted some deprecated html files Deleted chat
Added login required

Fixed request/create pass fragment styling
Fixed UI problems in login screen
Fixed request/create forms
Fixed signup
Fixed backend bugs (approval argument was missing "user" and Pass model didn't have a get_destinationTeacher method to get the correct destination teacher)

Added Checkin case for locationpass objects in the teacher_pass_fragment
Made start and end times not required (for srt passes)

Added tabs.js which consolidates tab switching code and makes tabs persistent across refresh via hashtags in the url
Changed teacher "all" tab to "old" tab
Had to recollect static files
Added animations for the plus sign when you click it
Fixed pass-card css so that they display in "table" form and are portions of the view size not fixed pixel dimensions.

Fixed primary button switching on page load for tabs.js
Added default case to tabs.js
Added icons to passes

Added "Location" and "SpecialSRTPass" models
Added Location option to signup form
Remove EditUserForm
Updated view security
Added location_home view and supporting files (html etc)
Made new api (The old one I made was really bad). This new api is not completely done however, it only has view for getting user data, passes and retrieving a single pass (of each type)
